public enum XMLTVGrabbersByCountry
extends java.lang.Enum<XMLTVGrabbersByCountry>

An enum to match the human-representation of a Nation (e.g. ITALY) with the corresponding XMLTV grabber (this is a command that will be used to download the schedule)
